information: Importing and exporting high quality unprocessed tobacco leaves is the core business of tutabaconatural.com. Our brand requires very high levels of quality from tobacco farmers and our unprocessed product is considered as a raw material, that has never been worked on by tobacco workers. We sell whole tobacco leaves, which means that their size, vein pattern and shape vary from harvest to harvest. They are usually heart-shaped or oval, with uncut edges.
